gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Timberwolves 118, Mavericks 110
gameRecap.excerpt: The Timberwolves defeated the Mavericks, 118-110. Anthony Edwards recorded a season-high 44 points, along with four assists and three rebounds for the Timberwolves, with Rudy Gobert adding 20 points and 11 rebounds in the victory. Tim Hardaway Jr. tallied 32 points and three rebounds for the Mavericks in the losing effort. The Timberwolves improve to 23-7 in the regular season, while the Mavericks fall to 18-14.
